				<p>The elderly gentleman from across the hall approached me.</p>

				<p>&#8220;When I was younger, I thought it would be horrible to get old,&#8221; he said. &#8220;I have finally proved myself right.&#8221;</p>

				<p>I laughed, and laughed, and laughed.</p>

				<p>I also pointed.</p>

		
		

